Metro,Transit,is,the,transportation,resource,for,the,Twin,Cities,offering,a,network,of,buses,light,rail,and,commuter,trains,as,well,as,additional,resources,for,those,using,alternate,forms,of,transportation,The,NexTrip,API,provides,users,with,real,time,data,about,vehicles,at,a,specified,stop,Data,can,include,departure,time,gate,route,terminal,direction,and,more,Information,in,the,NexTrip,API,is,updated,every,seconds,to,reflect,real,time,changes,in,transit,service,It,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,can,be,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON